item.title: User/ log in
item.dc:creator: @Vorro_Scape Vorro Scape
item.description:
@Vorro_Scape wrote:

Okay well you can find tons of servers in the server advertisement board, all you do is change your port by clicking files at the top of the moparscape and click change port and change it to the port the server is on. Then, type in the ip and log in with any username or passwords. Some servers may require hamachi. You can download it here, www.hamachi.cc
[br][size=1]Posted on: March 02, 2007, 10:39:56 PM[/size][hr]It easy to work hamachi, tho im kinda busy to explain, but there is tuts on it, if you cant find the tut then I suggest playing servers without hamachi for now.
